    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in truly incredible shape\u2014it honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car since day one, so it\u2019s spotless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been meticulously cared for and is ready for the road, this is definitely the one. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade E46 M3, showcasing the pinnacle of the S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six. This specimen features a perfectly synchronized Double VANOS system and individual throttle bodies that deliver instantaneous transient response. The mechanical integrity is absolute: the rear subframe has been structurally reinforced, rod bearings have been replaced with treated shells for longevity, and the ZF 6-speed manual gearbox offers short, tactile throws. The factory variable M differential lock ensures optimal torque distribution across the rear axle. This is a turnkey, collector-quality chassis with a pristine underside and zero mechanical parasitic loss. A rare opportunity for the discerning purist.",
